{
  "texts": [
    "This demonstrates that ReflecTool not only enhances the model's ability to select the appropriate domain-specific tools but also enables the agent to leverage the tool-wise reflection mechanism to provide better parameters when invoking tools, thereby maximizing their effectiveness.",
    "All the LLMs and MLLMs methods solve the task under the zero-shot settings while all the agentbased methods are one-shot to demonstrate the action format for the agents.",
    "Besides, considering that the multimodal tools can only be used in multimodal tasks, we remove the multimodal tools when agents are solving other types of tasks to save the cost of memory.",
    "All the experiments are run on two NVIDIA A100 80GB.",
    "The prompts of the optimization stage are shown in Figure 8 and Figure 9."
  ]
}